fr.gouv.vitam.common.thread

Class VitamThreadPoolExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.AbstractExecutorService
      • java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor
        • fr.gouv.vitam.common.thread.VitamThreadPoolExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Executor, ExecutorService, org.eclipse.jetty.util.thread.ThreadPool, org.glassfish.jersey.spi.ExecutorServiceProvider

    @Named(value="threadpool")
 @ManagedAsyncExecutor
public class VitamThreadPoolExecutor
extends ThreadPoolExecutor
implements org.eclipse.jetty.util.thread.ThreadPool, org.glassfish.jersey.spi.ExecutorServiceProvider
    Vitam ThreadPoolExecutor compatible with Jersey which copy the VitamSession from the main thread to the subthread
